00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:47.610
So this first graph here, y is
greater than or equal to

00:05:47.610 --> 00:05:50.560
negative x plus 15, this is this
top line, because it has

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:52.450
a higher y-intercept than
this other guy.

00:05:52.450 --> 00:05:54.060
This guy is 12.6.

