00:06:04.340 --> 00:06:05.085
So it's that line.

00:06:05.085 --> 00:06:07.750
And we want to be greater than
or equal to that line.

00:06:07.750 --> 00:06:10.430
So we want all of the values
of above that line,

00:06:10.430 --> 00:06:11.360
